[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ケガをしたときの薬の用意は……大丈夫そう。\n大砲の弾の準備はどうかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00260",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "最後の１発を調合中！\nとびっきりのを作ってるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00261",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "船で火事でも起こったらとんでもないね、こりゃ。\n引火したら大爆発できっと海に穴ができるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00262",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "食料の準備もした……身体を温めるものも作ったし、\n考えられるだけのものは用意したはず……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00263",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "でも正直、どんなに準備してもし足りない気がする……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00264",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……そうだね。こんなに準備しても、\nあの魔境を越えられるかどうかは、分からない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00265",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "いざというとき無事に戻れるよう、\n逃げるための道具も作っておいたほうがいいかもね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00266",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "それなら、陽動用に作ってる道具がそのまま使えるかも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00267",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "陽動用の道具？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00268",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あの魔物たち、どれだけ数がいるか分からない\nじゃないっすか？　まともに戦うのは愚策ってね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00269",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "だからおとりを出して、そっちに気を取られている隙に\n後ろをささっと通り抜けようって寸法よ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00270",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "いいね！　私もずっと考えてたんだよ。\n逃げのハイディちゃんは、できるだけ危険を避けたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00271",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "こっちのことなんか気にならないくらい\n目立つおとりがあれば、こっちは攻撃されないかもね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00272",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "ただ、まだちょっとハイディちゃんのお肌が\n「危ないよ！」って鳥肌立ってるんだよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00273",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "むむ……もう一工夫必要そうと？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00274",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "うん。そのおとりだけで、私たちの船を\nちゃんと見逃してくれるかなって不安はある",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00275",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "……じゃあ、その上で船を隠せれば\nいいってことかなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00276",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "船を隠す……か。なるほど。\nそれこそ、私おなじみの手が使えそうだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00277",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ハイディおなじみの手？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00278",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "なるほど、煙幕ですね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00279",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "船周辺を丸ごと包むような巨大な煙幕を張りつつ、\nおとりを出す……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00280",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "おとりは煙幕の中でも目立つものじゃないと\nいけませんね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00281",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そっか。じゃあ、考えていたおとりより\nもう一工夫必要かも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00282",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "うん、いい感じだ。保証はできないけど、\nハイディちゃんのお肌はいけそうだって言ってるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00283",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "大丈夫です。ハイディさんのことを信じます。\n私たち、何度も救われてきましたから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00284",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "それでは、最後の追い込みです！\n戦わずに突破するための道具……作りましょう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00285",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]